data.description:
Welcome to 7911 Rowland Ave, a charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom ranch home nestled in Kansas City, Kansas on a quite cul-de-sac street. This inviting home boasts a spacious two-car attached garage, complete with extra space for storage or a potential workshop. Tons of natural lighting and oversized rooms make this home feel extremely spacious. 

Lots of recent upgrades: new roof, new custom kitchen countertop with new sink, Stainless steel fridge, stainless steel dishwasher, new backsplash. Brand new AC and Furnace. Upgraded bathroom vanity. Hallways are oversized with lots of storage closets throughout. 

The home features a full basement, providing versatility and potential for customization to suit your unique preferences. Large open storage space off the garage can fit a whole car for reference. This is great for storage or could make for an easy access workshop off the garage.  Step outside of the walk out basement and discover the expansive backyard, adorned with mature, shady trees, offering a tranquil oasis for relaxation or entertaining. Front yard features beautiful evergreen shrubs and an assortment of pre annual flowers that bloom at different times in the year. 

Don't miss out on the chance to call this delightful abode your new home sweet home.
